Pollux Gateway Application
==========================

This program runs the network of sensor devices for the Pollux'nz City project.


Dependencies
============

 * libgcrypt    <http://www.gnu.org/s/libgcrypt/>
 * libjson-glib <http://live.gnome.org/JsonGlib>

Compilation
===========

 % make

You can put in environment a "DEFINE" variable having : 
 * VERBOSE
    to have more output
 * API_ESCAPED_MODE
    to change XBee API Mode from 1 to 2 (still untested)

Execution
=========

 % ./pollux_gateway

